Package de.sdc

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    This is the client which could receive commands from a server and forwards the commands to the caller
    CustomCommandHandler
    the implementations of this class could be used to handle custom commands received from clients
    Initializer
    abstract class that represents an object that is used to initilize the client
    NetworkUtil
    This class offers methods to send and receive objects over the network For faster serialization FST is used.
    Server<T extends Task,R extends ResultCommand>
    This class represents a server which is able to queue tasks, to distribute them to the clients and receive the results
    Task
    A task will be send from the server to the clients and defines what they should calculate
